="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/wojciech-dziedzic/" rel="tag">Wojciech Dziedzic</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Agustín Diassera, Alexander Polzin, Andrés Ibáñez, Andrés Máspero, Antonio Lozano, Antonio Magno, Anuschka Braun, Arcángel, Bárbara Lluch, Carlos Rodas, Coro Titular del Teatro Real, Daniel Kone, Darrell Grand Moultrie, Erin Caves, Federico García Lorca, Florian Bogner, Gun-Brit Barkmin, Haizam Fathy, Harold Torres, Isabella Gaudí, Jesús Méndez, José Antonio López, José San Antonio, Josep Miquel Ramón, Juan Manuel Cañizares, Klangforum Wien, Leonardo Cremaschi, Mack Sayer, Mauricio Sotelo, Mauro Lanza, Nicola Minssen, Pablo Heras-Casado, Patricia Barton, Pedro Pablo Prudencio, Peter Böhm, Robert Castro, Rubén Olmo, Samuel Echardour, Thomas Tatzl, Urs Schönebaum, William Isaac, Wojciech Dziedzic"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b41b40d04cc32e3e4f904f051c19deec" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Michele-Curnis-120x150.jpg" width="80" height="100" alt="Michele Curnis" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Michele Curnis"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-curnis/">View all articles by Michele Curnis</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera